Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji and Pudding's bloodbath wedding\Nfinally began.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down Big Mom, Luffy and the others allied with Bege\Nand broke the portrait of Mother Carmel,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}successfully making Big Mom shriek.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And memories of the past came back to Big Mom.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Charlotte Linlin, also known as Big Mom,\Nhas been...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...feared for her brute strength since she was a child\Nand was abandoned in Elbaph, country of the Giants.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There, she met Mother Carmel,\Na nun who was admired by everyone,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and lived happily with other orphans...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carmel... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may look like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! Jorul-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a god of Disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Birth of Mom!\NThe Day That Carmel Vanished!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin! Let me give you a coup de grace\Nwith my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Se...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jorul!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...m...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...la!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beardfall-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jorul-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Se... m... la!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has she done...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Catch her already!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rough her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get Semla?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some for the Festival\Nin the village storehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mother, what are you doing?!\N--It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gebur...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tstag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's a face in the fire!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I name you "Pandora"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feed her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious! It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simmer down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worked a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The god of the sun brought everything under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punish her... Don't think her as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do anything...\Nshe'll bring more disaster in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Jorul-{\i1}sama{\i}!\N--Get him treatment now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beardhill-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you let me do it, Carmel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jorul is my friend who I fought with for 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too old... I don't think he can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a warrior isn't about living long...\NIt's about how you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to bring it to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who defies Elbaph's laws\Ncan't be forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!\NBut even if she can't be forgiven,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since the poor Linlin was abandoned by the whole world\Nand ended up in the House of Lambs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave here along with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carmel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beardhill-{\i1}sama{\i}! Please kill Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we pardon her\Nafter she's done such a horrible thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your Elbaph pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, why don't you get out of my sight now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Beardfall-{\i1}sama{\i}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jorul, the hero of the Giants, died...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A god of Disaster named Linlin...\NCarmel's miracle...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The details of that day...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...spread across a small number of\Nthe Giant nations all over the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with the orphans of the House of Lambs\Nwho refused to be separated from their Mother,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Charlotte Linlin\Nwho became the enemy of all the Giants,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother Carmel left Elbaph.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And they all started a new life\Nat the new House of Lambs.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done! Is this good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than enough.\NI'm sorry for asking these favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without your help,\NI couldn't build a house deep in the mountains like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. To be honest,\NI don't wanna see Linlin's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're the Holy Mother even for the Giants, Carmel.\NYou can ask anything of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To relieve the children's growing concerns,\NCarmel tried to smile even more.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A few days after leaving Elbaph,\Nthey were the same as they'd always been...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Linlin's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The House of Lambs was filled with\Nthe children's laughter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after the house while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time will you be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return as soon as I finish buying groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shortcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A set of cards!\N--Toy swords for samurai fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Mother! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A legend grew about the House of Lambs.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any troubled child will be born again\Nwith Mother's help and meet good foster parents...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Have I ever stood you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to leave Elbaph...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how much I didn't wanna let go of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it. She's only five now but she's already so\Nexceptional that she could destroy half of the Elbaph village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the price is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Navy,\Nshe'd become a vice admiral or a fleet admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Cipher Pol,\Nshe'd be the toughest shield for the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trafficking kids for 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the greatest product we've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,37 years ago, I put on a good show with the Navy\Nand snuck into Elbaph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John Giant became\Nthe Navy's first Giant soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of my connections!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been fooling the kids\Nat the House of Lambs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and selling fresh orphans once every two years\Nto the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're perfect for intelligence agents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orphans can't be traced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right!\NI'll try to come up with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a lot of work to act as the Holy Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:33.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,MOTHER CARMEL - AN ORPHAN SELLER\N(UNDERWORLD NAME: MOUNTAIN HAG)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking to take this occasion to retire from the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this'll be my last deal. I need you to pay me in full!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you all wanna sing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Binks's Brew"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's a pirates' song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NWe'll become pirates some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's very cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time to ship out Binks's Brew!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sea wind blows to where, who knows?\NThe waves will be our guide!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O'er across the ocean's tide, the sunset is goin' wild{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See the sky! Birds singing in circles passing by!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'll sell you brats to the Government\Nrather than pirates!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bid farewell to weaver's town!\NSay so long to port renowned!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sing a song, it won't be long before we're casting off!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cross the gold and silver waves, changin' into water sprays!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sailing out on our journey to the ends of the sea!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hand over the rest of the kids along with Linlin\Nto the Navy tomorrow, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that,\NI'll celebrate your special day so much, Linlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come, this way!\N--Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! But what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We piled up your favorite sweet, Semla,\Nand made this Croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Croquembouche? Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a tea party!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tea party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll spend time gracefully sitting around tables,\Ndrinking tea and eating sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!\NI wanna have that! A tea party!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's make tea.\N--Join us, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eat as much as you want!\N--Eat, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She eats so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tea party's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy! It's so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, Mother Carmel vanished.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the day Linlin had the happiest birthday\Never in her life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The special friends at the House of Lambs,\Nwho had similar backgrounds.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The open-minded and generous Mother\Nthat she loved.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being surrounded by everyone's smiles\Nand eating her favorite sweet, sweet birthday cake,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Linlin couldn't hold back her tears.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you like, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat... I'll eat it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:20:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a lovely day...\NTears blurred her eyes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, don't rush, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay together and have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We'll stay together forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good girl, Linlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a lovely birthday.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so happy!\NI was carried away so I even bit the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!\NI'll never forget about today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, Mother Carmel...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...disappeared all of a sudden.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?! Everyone! In the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Mother...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did you disappear all of a sudden?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motha! Where're ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment to assassinate\Nthe Emperor of the Sea finally comes!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The enraged Big Mom's shriek rings out,\Nand when Bege's deadly poison gas weapon fires,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy's allied force's mission finally comes to a climax!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Launcher Blasts! The Moment of Big Mom's Assassination!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
